    {
        "class": "General",
        "text": "Now, let's expand the right side:"
    },
    {
        "class": "General",
        "text": "First term: (An + B)(n\u00b2 - 2n + 2) = An(n\u00b2 - 2n + 2) + B(n\u00b2 - 2n + 2)\n= A n\u00b3 - 2A n\u00b2 + 2A n + B n\u00b2 - 2B n + 2B."
