    {
        "class": "General",
        "text": "Second term: (Cn + D)(n\u00b2 + 2n + 2) = Cn(n\u00b2 + 2n + 2) + D(n\u00b2 + 2n + 2)\n= C n\u00b3 + 2C n\u00b2 + 2C n + D n\u00b2 + 2D n + 2D."
