        "text": "(An + B)/(n\u00b2 + 2n + 2) + (Cn + D)/(n\u00b2 - 2n + 2) = (0\u00b7n + (-1/4))/(n\u00b2 + 2n + 2) + (0\u00b7n + 1/4)/(n\u00b2 - 2n + 2)"
